    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This seal is drawn from the target's cursed seal out onto a small circle on the floor, after which it contracts and forms a barrier around the cursed seal. The seal has one charge per level or HD of the target, and each time they make a Control Cursed Seal check to resist an involuntary transformation, one charge is consumed to grant a +8 bonus to the check. Once all charges are used, the seal disappears. If the target becomes a willing bearer of the cursed seal, the seal is destroyed.</p>\n\n\n\n",
